{"type":null,"faqId":38522,"title":"设置日期和时间","answer":"<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p5{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n</style>\n<div>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125578\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">”“设置”。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">在“全部设置”页签下，点击“日期和时间”。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">在“日期和时间”界面，您可以：</span>\n</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">\n</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击“自动确定日期和时间”开关，开启或关闭使用网络时间。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">\n</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击“自动确定时区”开关，开启或关闭使用网络时区。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">\n</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击“使用 24 小时格式”开关，在 24小时制与 12 小时制之间切换。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">\n</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击“选择日期格式”，选择手机上显示的日期格式。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">\n</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击“双时钟”，选择漫游时在锁屏界面显示双时钟。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125579\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none; font-size: 10.5pt; \">部分网络运营商不支持手动设置日期和时间。</span>\n</span><br>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\"></p>\n<p class=\"p5\"></p>\n<p class=\"p5\"></p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":1,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3802","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441448688000,"seriesProductName":"GRA-CL00,GRA-CL10,GRA-TL00,GRA-UL00,GRA-UL10","visitedTimes":86,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"设置日期和时间","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}